## Outputs

Per S12 (Study artifact format):

```
studies/<target-slug>/
├── BLUEPRINT.md         # the domain-agnostic spec (this skill's headline output)
├── evidence/            # screenshots, downloaded docs, response snapshots
├── notes/               # raw per-mode notes (raw-product.md, raw-paper.md, ...)
├── questions.md         # open questions, tagged
└── citations.md         # every external claim with source + retrieval date
```

`TRANSPOSITION.md`, `BUILD-LOG.md`, and `FIDELITY-EVAL.md` are written by the
**downstream** Family J skills — do not create empty stubs here.

