## Dependencies

- **S12 (study artifact format)** — this skill writes the canonical layout
  consumed by `/transpose`, `/clone-and-twist`, `/recipe`. Frontmatter fields
  (`target`, `mode`, `version`, `derived_from`) are load-bearing.
- **S13 (mechanism-fidelity contract)** — this skill **proposes** candidate
  mechanism properties in BLUEPRINT.md §9. `/clone-and-twist` finalizes them
  into the `evals/fidelity/<slug>.jsonl` contract.
- `/browse` — `product`, `app`, `api` modes.
- `markitdown` — `paper` mode PDF/HTML ingestion.
- `/scrape` — within-bounds public-content fetch (`product` mode docs).
- `huggingface-skills:hugging-face-paper-publisher` — paper-mode citation formatting.
- `lib/study-extractors/{product,paper,code,app,api}.ts` — per-mode extractors (planned).
- `lib/study-artifacts.ts` — shared parser for the S12 frontmatter (planned).

